data.description: Step into this stunning home with an extraordinary display of curb appeal that will instantly capture your attention. The paver driveway adorned with an artistic design welcomes you with an elegant touch. The two-car garage offers not only convenience but also an attractive addition to the overall aesthetics of the property. Enjoy maintenance-free living in this 2 BR, 2 bath home which boasts an inviting open floor plan, ensuring that natural light generously bathes the entire living space. As you enter, the formal living and dining areas greet you with their sophistication and high ceilings, creating an atmosphere of grandeur. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is adorned with rich wood cabinets, gleaming stainless steel appliances, and exquisite granite countertops. There's an eat-in space where you can enjoy casual meals, and it seamlessly connects to the family room. A sliding door leads to the Florida room, perfect for enjoying the beautiful outdoors while remaining comfortable indoors. The primary bedroom is a sanctuary, featuring an ensuite bath that's both spacious and opulent. It boasts two separate vanities, a deep soaking tub for relaxation, a dedicated makeup space, and marble countertops. The walk-in tiled shower, enclosed with glass doors, adds a touch of modernity to the timeless design. For those in need of additional space, there's a bonus room that could effortlessly serve as a third bedroom, office, or recreational space. The entire house is graced with a harmonious blend of wood and tile flooring, no carpet. This home is not just a place to reside; it's a lifestyle. This 55+ community offers an array of amenities, including tennis courts, a baseball field, a sparkling swimming pool with a spa, clubhouse, restaurant, and fitness center, all nestled beautifully on a scenic golf course. It's an invitation to an active and luxurious way of life, where you can relish the beauty of your surroundings and the comfort of your home. Schedule your showing today!
